{"type":"message","id":"2a0c51a9","parentId":"4518c29b","timestamp":"2026-03-30T06:16:05.405Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我遇到了飞书 API 权限问题。我已经为您发送了授权卡片，请按照以下步骤操作：\n\n1. **在聊天窗口中查看授权卡片**（应该已经显示在对话中）\n2. **点击卡片中的授权按钮**\n3. **确认授权以下 3 个权限**：\n   - 通讯录读取权限\n   - 其他相关权限\n\n授权完成后，我就可以正常使用飞书相关功能了。\n\n如果您没有看到授权卡片，也可以让管理员访问以下链接进行授权：\nhttps://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a940ae98b3bb1bd8/auth?q=contact%3Acontact.base%3Areadonly&op_from=openapi&token_type=tenant"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774851360214}}
