{"type":"message","id":"0276c4f4","parentId":"b564709b","timestamp":"2026-03-30T06:17:06.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我目前无法直接生成图片。我没有集成图像生成模型（如 DALL-E、Midjourney 或 Stable Diffusion）。\n\n不过我可以帮你：\n\n1. **搜索图片** - 使用网络搜索找到相关图片\n2. **下载/处理图片** - 如果你提供图片链接，我可以下载或处理\n3. **创建图表/可视化** - 使用代码生成简单的数据可视化图表\n\n如果你需要 AI 生成图片，建议使用：\n- Midjourney\n- DALL-E 3 (ChatGPT Plus)\n- Stable Diffusion\n- 百度文心一格、通义万相等国内工具\n\n有什么我可以帮你的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774851417988}}
