hon, JavaScript, TypeScript, Go, Rust, and more. Just tell me what you need.\",\n            \"skills\": \"I have access to various skills/tools: web search, file management, calendar/schedule management, messaging, browser automation, and more. I can also use specialized skills for Feishu, weather, and other services.\",\n            \"tools\": \"I can use tools for web search, browser automation, file operations,"}},{"type":"text","text":" calendar"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774851854150}}
