{"type":"message","id":"2759e447","parentId":"1e43c515","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:33:32.410Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-30 16:28:04 GMT+8] Exec completed (keen-cov, code 0) :: ns/feishu/node_modules/@larksuiteoapi/node-sdk/package.json /home/admin/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-qqbot/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/package.json /home/admin/.…\nSystem: [2026-03-30 16:33:31 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_ea1c6c04083c10886bdd141a0cc60ff9 [msg:om_x100b53971b614960b398da872224d43]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53971b614960b398da872224d43\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_ea1c6c04083c10886bdd141a0cc60ff9\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_ea1c6c04083c10886bdd141a0cc60ff9\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-30 16:33 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_ea1c6c04083c10886bdd141a0cc60ff9\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_ea1c6c04083c10886bdd141a0cc60ff9\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_ea1c6c04083c10886bdd141a0cc60ff9\"\n}\n```\n\nmake a game that is a 2d pvp game similar to super smash bros in an html file ,with pixle art and controlls with the keyboard, make it have sound effect and a health bar, multiple characters and maps and make it ask you to give a username each time to play and display that aboave the player when playing,use html and save it in your server"}],"timestamp":1774859612406}}
{"type":"message","id":"8d79c3dc","parentId":"2759e447","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:37:47.870Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✗\n\nI'm working on creating a 2D PvP fighting game similar to Super Smash Bros with pixel art, keyboard controls, sound effects, health bars, multiple characters and maps. This will be a comprehensive HTML file with all features you requested."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.write:39","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/admin/.openclaw/workspace/smash-bros-game.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Pixel Smash Bros - PvP Fighting Game</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);\n            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        #gameContainer {\n            position: relative;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        canvas {\n            border: 4px solid #e94560;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.5);\n            image-rendering: pixelated;\n        }\n\n        #ui {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            width: 800px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            padding: 10px;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .playerInfo {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .playerName {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);\n        }\n\n        .healthBar {\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 25px;\n            background: #333;\n            border: 3px solid #fff;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .healthFill {\n            height: 100%;\n            transition: width 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .healthFill.p1 { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff4444, #ff8888); }\n        .healthFill.p2 { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4444ff, #8888ff); }\n\n        .damagePercent {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            color: #ffd700;\n        }\n\n        #menuScreen, #characterSelect, #usernameScreen {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            z-index: 100;\n        }\n\n        .title {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            color: #e94560;\n            text-shadow: 4px 4px 8px rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.8);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }\n        }\n\n        .menuButton {\n            padding: 15px 40px;\n            margin: 10px;\n            font-size: 20px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560, #ff6b6b);\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            color: white;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s;\n            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .menuButton:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.1);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.8);\n        }\n\n        .characterGrid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .characterCard {\n            width: 120px;\n            height: 150px;\n            background: #333;\n            border: 3px solid #666;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s;\n        }\n\n        .characterCard:hover, .characterCard.selected {\n            border-color: #e94560;\n            transform: scale(1.1);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .characterIcon {\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 60px;\n            image-rendering: pixelated;\n        }\n\n        .characterName {\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n\n        .usernameInput {\n            padding: 15px;\n            font-size: 20px;\n            border: 3px solid #e94560;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            background: #1a1a2e;\n            color: white;\n            margin: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;\n        }\n\n        #controls {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .controlSection {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin: 0 30px;\n            vertical-align: top;\n        }\n\n        .controlTitle {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #e94560;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .key {\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding: 5px 10px;\n            margin: 2px;\n            background: #444;\n            border: 2px solid #666;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n        }\n\n        .hidden { display: none !important; }\n\n        #winnerScreen {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);\n            display: none;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            z-index: 200;\n        }\n\n        .winnerText {\n            font-size: 64px;\n            color: #ffd700;\n            text-shadow: 4px 4px 8px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.8);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .mapPreview {\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 120px;\n            background: #333;\n            border: 3px solid #666;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            margin: 10px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s;\n        }\n\n        .mapPreview:hover, .mapPreview.selected {\n            border-color: #e94560;\n            transform: scale(1.05);\n        }\n\n        .mapGrid {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin: 20px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"gameContainer\">\n        <div id=\"ui\">\n            <div class=\"playerInfo\">\n                <div class=\"playerName\" id=\"p1Name\">Player 1</div>\n                <div class=\"healthBar\">\n                    <div class=\"healthFill p1\" id=\"p1Health\" style=\"width: 100%;\"></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"damagePercent\" id=\"p1Damage\">0%</div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #e94560; font-weight: bold;\">VS</div>\n            <div class=\"playerInfo\">\n                <div class=\"playerName\" id=\"p2Name\">Player 2</div>\n                <div class=\"healthBar\">\n                    <div class=\"healthFill p2\" id=\"p2Health\" style=\"width: 100%;\"></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"damagePercent\" id=\"p2Damage\">0%</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <canvas id=\"gameCanvas\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\"></canvas>\n\n        <!-- Username Screen -->\n        <div id=\"usernameScreen\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Enter Your Name</div>\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"p1Username\" class=\"usernameInput\" placeholder=\"Player 1 Name\""}},{"type":"text","text":" maxlength"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774859612409}}
